title: 249: NFL's best gifts, Top 5 NFL Executives in 2017
itunes:title: 249: NFL's best gifts, Top 5 NFL Executives in 2017
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks rank their favorites to win front office executive of the year (00:52). The guys also get into the holiday spirit by revealing their NFL naughty and nice lists (10:28), ranking the best gifts the league received this season (18:43), and picking a franchise that should visit Santa's workshop in the offseason (16:03).
